name: JavaScript
description: Become a better web developer by building JavaScript projects.

name: Running
description: Whether for marathon training or just daily exercise, improve your health by running.

name: Watercolor
description: Break out your best brushes, paints, and thick paper and get painting!

name: Exploration
description: Explore new places around your neighborhood, city, or beyond.

name: Writing
description: Writing a little every day, you could finish the first draft of a novel!

name: Reading
description: The average person only reads 2 books a year. Be way above average.

name: Yoga
description: Improve your physical and spiritual well-being by practicing yoga regularly.

name: Connection
description: Keep in touch or reconnect with friends, family, and people you know. Say I love you, thank you, or just hello.

name: Rejection
description: Get rejected on purpose! Get used to it, learn from it, and grow beyond your fear.

name: Gratitude
description: Keep a gratitude journal and write down the things you're grateful for. You can't write too many!

name: Weight Loss
description: Eat and drink healthy, exercise, sleep well, and lose weight the right way.

name: Romance
description: Romance your partner like you did when you'd just met.

name: YouTube
description: Creating videos consistently is the key to building up a YouTube following.

name: Speed Painting
description: Do 15-20 minute paintings in the medium of your choice to improve your use of color, space, lighting, and other design elements.

name: Saving
description: Open up a savings account and start putting money away.
